action.description: The action to display in the card header.

classes.description: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.

component.description: The component used for the root node. Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.

disableTypography.description: If true, subheader and title won't be wrapped by a Typography component. This can be useful to render an alternative Typography variant by wrapping the title text, and optional subheader text with the Typography component.

slotProps.description: The props used for each slot inside.

slots.description: The components used for each slot inside.

subheaderTypographyProps.description: These props will be forwarded to the subheader (as long as disableTypography is not true).

sx.description: The system prop that allows defining system overrides as well as additional CSS styles.

titleTypographyProps.description: These props will be forwarded to the title (as long as disableTypography is not true).

slotDescriptions.action: The component that renders the action slot.
slotDescriptions.avatar: The component that renders the avatar slot.
slotDescriptions.content: The component that renders the content slot.
slotDescriptions.root: The component that renders the root slot.
slotDescriptions.subheader: The component that renders the subheader slot (as long as disableTypography is not true). Follow this guide to learn more about the requirements for this component.
slotDescriptions.title: The component that renders the title slot (as long as disableTypography is not true). Follow this guide to learn more about the requirements for this component.
